data.description: This Home has it all Location, Privacy and lots of nature in your backyard. When you enter into the home, there will be two bedrooms and a bathroom on the right. A little further will take you to the guest bedroom and a bathroom on the left. Continue walking to the dining room and family room, which has vaulted ceilings and natural light shining into the open floorplan. Past the dining room is the kitchen with a gas range, plenty of cabinets and countertops for those who love cooking. Enjoy a morning cup of coffee or relax at the end of the day with a glass of wine looking at nature right at your back sliding glass door. The master bedroom overlooks the back yard with nature all around. Remolded bathroom with shiplap, new lighting, flooring, and more. The master bathroom has both a garden tub and separate shower stall. Other features, other than the master bathroom being remodeled 2 years ago, New AC was installed November 2020, a new roof installed in 2021 the home is also equipped with a water softener. Bridgewater Crossing is a Short-Term Rental Community, and you'll have your own fishing pond in your back yard. Plus, Bridgewater Crossing has great amenities - pool, tennis courts, basketball court, volleyball court, and a picnic area. A wonderful location for shopping, restaurants, golf, the amusement parks, and major roadways. Set your appointment today or DM Listing agents for more information.
